snippet.title: WWF Legends 2.0 - Download.
snippet.description:
WWF Legends 2.0 - Download.

The wait is OVER! WWF Legends 2.0 is now available to download at the Wrestling Legends Forum and Old School Reunion. See the description below for more information.

WWF Legends Team: Iccotracs, Orson, FTW JMe, WldFb, wwefan4life2, mikehollow, jazz and outlaw21.

A special thank you to everyone at WLF, OSR and the now defunct NMZ, for all of your support over the years.

WWF Legends is a modification of WWF No Mercy, emulated on Project 64. 

Download WWF Legends 2.0 at any of the following websites;
WLF: http://thewrestlinglegendsforum.com
OSR: http://s4.zetaboards.com/Old_Skool_Reunion

Download a higher quality version of this video here;
http://speedy.sh/eJREa/WWF-Legends-2.0-CV.rar
